SUMMARY:700 Level Student Showcase
DTSTAMP:20260326T122438Z
DTSTART:20260401T190000Z
DESCRIPTION:Witness the creation of believable characters\\\, inspiring sce
	nes\\\, and some improv magic by 700 level class.\\n\\n\\n\\nJoin the adva
	nced students in our 700 class and witness them blossom with new improv sk
	ills. Under the guidance of our expert improv teachers\\\, 700 students ar
	e learning new narrative formats and enhancing their skills by working in 
	an ensemble. You get to see the fruits of their efforts by witnessing the 
	creation of believable characters\\\, inspiring scenes\\\, and some improv
